        "href": "https://developer.apple.com/tutorials/swiftui?ref=madewithvuejs.com"
      }}>{`Apple`}</a>{` describes SwiftUI is a modern way to declare user interfaces for any Apple platform. Unlike imperative UI layout tools like Interface Builder and Auto Layout, the declarative nature of SwiftUI Views allows developers to concentrate on composition and state.`}</p>
    <div class="rounded-md bg-blue-50 p-4">
  <div class="flex">
